{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Apply the Human Rights Act retrospectively",
        "additional_details": "I believe this could potentially allow victims of sexual exploitation, whose cases weren\u2019t properly investigated, to obtain justice for the failure to investigate, where this was before the introduction of the Human Rights Act. \r\n \r\nVictims of abuse don\u2019t always come forward until many years later and deserve justice.",
        "background": "I think the Government should legislate for full retrospective application of the Human Rights Act.",
